	<message label="002" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Explain" target="actor" targetSpec="" />我正在製作
<tag a="125" b="0" arg="0x0" />。<pageBreak /><anim id="AbsentMindedness" target="actor" targetSpec="" />因為之前仰望夜空的時候，<delay20 />
突然有個想法<delay8 />
從我的腦海中冒出<tag a="110" b="0" /></message>
	<message label="003" attrib="00 00 02 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="QuestionMark" target="actor" targetSpec="" />想要我為你特別開課嗎？<delay frames="40" />
<anim id="Serious" target="actor" targetSpec="" />教你怎麼製作<tag a="110" b="0" /><delay20 /><tag a="110" b="10" />風
<anim id="Grin" target="actor" targetSpec="" /><tag a="125" b="0" arg="0x0" />！</message>
	<message label="003_a" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00">拜託你！</message>
	<message label="003_b" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00">應該先不用<tag a="110" b="0" /></message>
	<message label="007" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="ShyBoy" target="actor" targetSpec="" />算是吧<tag a="110" b="0" /><delay20 />
那<delay20 />我要繼續做囉，<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="008" attrib="00 00 01 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Shocked" target="actor" targetSpec="" />咦？<delay20 />　
你也知道<tag a="125" b="0" arg="0x0" />的
