<anim id="Grin" target="actor" targetSpec="" />這就是心心相印吧，<delay frames="40" /><anim id="BigSmile" target="actor" targetSpec="" />哈哈～！</message>
	<message label="010" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="OhGeez" target="actor" targetSpec="" /><tag a="110" b="0" />不過，<delay20 />
