	<message label="018" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="EmotEnd" target="actor" targetSpec="" />請<tag a="110" b="4" /><delay20 />
務必挑戰看看喔！<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="019" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Eh" target="actor" targetSpec="" />對了對了，<delay20 />我其實有把製作方法寫成筆記喔。<delay frames="40" />
<anim id="ShyBoy" target="actor" targetSpec="" />因為我想讓更多人知道<delay8 />
<tag a="125" b="0" arg="0x0" />的美好嘛。<pageBreak /><anim id="EmotEnd" target="actor" targetSpec="" />如果你身邊有朋友<delay20 />
想要知道製作方法，<delay20 />
<anim id="Hello" target="actor" targetSpec="" />就請你把這份筆記送給對方吧？<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="020" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="AbsentMindedness" target="actor" targetSpec="" />希望能讓更多的人製作<delay8 />
<tag a="125" b="0" arg="0x0" />，<delay20 />
並且展露笑容，<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="021" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Explain" target="actor" targetSpec="" />這邊有我寫好的<delay20 /><delay8 />
<tag a="125" b="0" arg="0x0" />製作方法，<delay frames="40" />
<anim id="Greeting" target="actor" targetSpec="" />只要看著這個製作，就沒問題了！</message>
	<message label="030" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Explain" target="actor" targetSpec="" />如果想製作跟我一樣的東西，<delay20 />
那就得先準備南瓜才行。<delay20 />
<anim id="Nodding" target="actor" targetSpec="" />你先去種南瓜吧，<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="031" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="FaintSmile" target="actor" targetSpec="" />順帶一提，如果想要進行改造的話，<delay20 />
就必須準備好<delay20 />
對應顏色的南瓜才行，<tag a="110" b="6" />。<pageBreak /><anim id="Explain" target="actor" targetSpec="" />只要好好培育南瓜，
就能種出很多不同顏色的果實。<delay20 />
<anim id="Explain" target="actor" targetSpec="" />越是照顧就越覺得它們可愛，很開心喔。</message>
	<message label="032" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Greeting" target="actor" targetSpec="" /><tag a="110" b="4" />，我等你很久囉。<delay frames="40" />
<anim id="FaintSmile" target="actor" targetSpec="" />我有好好保管<delay20 />
剛剛沒能交給你的物品喔，<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="033" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Shocked" target="actor" targetSpec="" />等等<tag a="110" b="0" />你說你已經知道<delay20 />
<anim id="QuestionMark" target="actor" targetSpec="" />跟這一樣的方程式了？<pageBreak /><anim id="ShyBoy" target="actor" targetSpec="" />我還想說如果你不知道的話，<delay20 />
就能向你分享這個方程式呢。<delay20 />
看來已經沒那個必要了<tag a="110" b="0" /></message>
	<message label="034" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Smiling" target="actor" targetSpec="" />如果是那樣的話，<delay20 />
反正我還有多餘的材料，<delay20 />
就分一點給你吧，<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="035" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Hello" target="actor" targetSpec="" />沐浴著<tag a="110" b="8" />上的陽光，<delay20 />
